_sText:
Short bhop map I made within the last week. It's nowhere near perfect but I think that it can be good fun especially for players that are capable of keeping their speed throughout the whole map.
Run Time between 1 - 2 minutes. Possible on Scroll and MaxVel, probably annoying on MaxVel though.

This is my first bhop map and feedback is greatly appreciated.
In the future I might create some more detailed maps too.

Cheers,
Netcode
